data.description: Introducing 11803 Old Spanish Trail, a charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home nestled within the highly sought-after neighborhood of Santa Fe Trails. This home is conveniently located, offering short commutes and close proximity to excellent dining and shopping options. Step into an inviting interior showcasing new hardwood flooring and stylish lighting that illuminates the space. The kitchen includes granite countertops and stainless steel appliances with freshly painted cabinetry. Enjoy the cozy ambience of the fireplace which is perfect for cooler evenings during this season. The primary bedroom has a sizeable ensuite bathroom and generous walk-in closet. Occupying a large corner lot with a newly fenced backyard, the property offers ample open space. This outdoor space invites for leisure and entertaining, complete with a patio for outdoor gatherings, and a shed for added storage. The property also features a driveway leading to an attached 2-car garage. Schedule your showing today!!
